text:
Hi all, 

Could you recommend any SEO-friendly Wordpress plugins (or other tools) for interactive tables and charts?

I've been writing a lot of technical content lately. The project I'm working on uses plain Wordpress (not even Gutenberg) with a template. It's very fast but also basic. 

The content would benefit greatly from data visualisation, preferably interactive (rearrangeable tables, etc.). I've been looking at my options, and there are many. So I thought I'd ask here first, as some of you might have experience with such tools. 

Thanks in advance for your recommendations!
